            <p>The evening after the evaluation test found Naruto at the memorial stone, a place he'd visited more frequently since his return. The names etched there seemed to watch him, silent witnesses to the cost of the shinobi life. Jiraiya had taught him about the stone, about the friends and comrades Kakashi had lost.</p>
            
