                        <p>The final stage of Winston's reeducation was Room 101, where each prisoner faced their worst fear. For Winston, it was rats. Faced with a cage of hungry rats that would be attached to his face, Winston finally broke completely, betraying Julia and accepting the Party's absolute power.</p>
